  "title": "Forklift driver",
  "description": "<p>Job Summary:</p><p>We are seeking a skilled and reliable Forklift Driver to join our dynamic team in our warehousing and logistics facility. The successful candidate will play a crucial role in ensuring efficient material handling and maintaining a safe work environment.</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>* Operate forklifts to load, unload, and transport production items within the facility</p><p>* Accurately produce, pack, and stack products on pallets</p><p>* Maintain a clean and organized workspace</p><p>* Collaborate with team members to ensure smooth operations</p><p>* Perform additional tasks as assigned by the supervisor</p><p>Job Requirements:</p><p>* Minimum 1-year experience in forklift operation</p><p>* Valid Forklift Driving License</p><p>* Strong attention to detail and commitment to safety protocols</p><p>* Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and adapt to changing priorities</p><p>Benefits & Perks:</p><p>* Competitive salary package at $1900-$2800</p><p>* Opportunities for skill development and career advancement</p><p>* Inclusive and multicultural work environment</p><p>Additional Information:</p><p>* Work Location: NO.9 SENOKO CRESCENT SINGAPORE 758265</p><p>* Full-time position</p><p>* Working hours and salary range to be discussed during the interview process</p><p>Whatsapp or contact 88571530 to schedule interview.</p>",
